<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMA522_05_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_05_su.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_05_su_0004">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="2" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                            <span>4</span>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        와
                        <span class="operation_box">
                            <span>4</span>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                        의 크기를 비교해 봅시다.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <div class="input_area">

                <article class="page page_1">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                <span>4&times;1</span>
                                과 비교하여
                                <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                    <span>4&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>2</span>
                                        <span>5</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                와 
                                <span class="operation_box">
                            <span>4</span>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                                를 각각 어림셈해 보세요.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="input_area">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <div class="example_box">
                                <p lang="y">                                    
                                    <span class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                                        <span class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                            <span class="operation_box ml_0">
                                                <span>4</span>
                                                <span>&times;</span>
                                                <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                            </span>
                                            는 4&times;1보다 더 작고&nbsp;
                                            <span class="operation_box">
                                                <span>4</span>
                                                <span>&times;</span>
                                                <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                                    <span>1</span>
                                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                                </span>
                                            </span>
                                            는 4&times;1보다 더 클 것 같습니다.                                            
                                        </span>
                                    </span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hint flex align_center dir_col f24r">
                            <span>1을 기준으로</span>
                            <span class="flex align_center">
                                <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                와&nbsp;
                                <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                </span>
                                의 크기를 생각해 봐.
                            </span>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                </div>
                                와
                                <div class="operation_box">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                를 각각 계산해 보세요.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- <div class="flex align_center gap_4" lang="y">
                            <span>4&times;</span><span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>와
                            <span>4&times;1</span><span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>를 각각 계산해
                            보세요.
                        </div> -->
                    </h3>
                    <div class="input_area m_auto">
                        <div class="question_box">
                            <div class="flex align_end gap_50 m_auto mt_40">

                                <span class="operation_box f32b">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>

                                    <span>=</span>
                                    <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="1(3)/(5)"
                                            data-answer-multi='{"values": ["1(3)/(5)", "(8)/(5)"]}' data-multi-hint="y"
                                            text-align="center" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                        <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                        <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                                        <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                        <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                        <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                                    </div>
                                </span>

                                <span class="operation_box f32b">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>=</span>
                                    <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="5(3)/(5)"
                                            data-answer-multi='{"values": ["5(3)/(5)", "(28)/(5)"]}' data-multi-hint="y"
                                            text-align="center" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                        <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                        <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                                        <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                        <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                        <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                                    </div>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_3">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                </div>
                                와
                                <div class="operation_box">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>&times;</span>
                                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                의 크기를 비교하여 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="input_area">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <div class="example_box">
                                <p>(자연수)×(진분수)는 (자연수)×1보다 더 작고, (자연수)×(대분수)는 (자연수)×1보다 더 큽니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <!-- 예시 필드에서 사용 -->
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>